verses.verse: Beasts and all cattle; Creeping things and flying fowl;
Kings of the earth and all peoples; Princes and all judges of the earth;
Both young men and maidens; Old men and children.
Let them praise the name of the LORD, For His (Is. 44:23; 49:13) name alone is exalted; His glory is above the earth and heaven.
And He (Ps. 8:1) has exalted the horn of His people, The praise of (1 Sam. 2:1; Ps. 75:10) all His saintsâ€” Of the children of Israel, (Ps. 149:9) A people near to Him. Praise the LORD!
(Praise to God for His Salvation and Judgment) Praise the LORD! (Lev. 10:3; Eph. 2:17) Sing to the LORD a new song, And His praise in the assembly of saints.
